{"tid":1278300,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"金鐘拆義士祭壇老嘢住天水圍","createTime":"2019-07-02T11:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T12:54:20.000Z","uid":37516,"like":125,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"ed12de7d81728baa2cf85588f40843dfdce18084","tid":1278300,"uid":37516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:57:32.000Z","msg":"朋友今日下午 1-2:00 見到佢，喺「天澤商場薩莉亞」同佢啲老嘢fd食緊野，身穿片段一樣嘅藍色衫。<br />\n<br />\n個死老鬼好大聲講自己俾人點晒相，跟住講佢嗰日參加撐警大聯盟，再點樣一手一腳拆爛祭壇啲英勇事蹟俾佢啲fd聽，<br />\n我朋友聽到有人咁講即刻擰轉面，一見就係佢，影相影唔到近鏡，因為一影近就一定會見到，我朋友帶住個小朋友太近唔可以冒險。<br />\n<br />\n請各位手足住天水圍嘅留意吓，尤其是天澤商場附近嘅屋村。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YGogVAa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYGogVAa.png&h=230b2e44&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f045280565861e218b7b4a6abccf09fca9f73cf0","tid":1278300,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:59:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36672fe9f539633f2bffe371ac06177909b1bff4","tid":1278300,"uid":37516,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:59:25.000Z","msg":"打少咗一句：佢嗰陣時係話自己預咗俾人尋仇點相，但係要做嘅都要做"},{"pid":"009cfb1cdc33acc44d100f6bd14ef1aa7481ab65","tid":1278300,"uid":155682,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"quote":{"pid":"36672fe9f539633f2bffe371ac06177909b1bff4","tid":1278300,"uid":37516,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:59:25.000Z","msg":"打少咗一句：佢嗰陣時係話自己預咗俾人尋仇點相，但係要做嘅都要做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:01:55.000Z","msg":"冇人會尋佢仇，但壇主每晚都會探下佢同佢屋企人"},{"pid":"b1f34412697120f336575ea5fbdf67494abe2050","tid":1278300,"uid":152432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:02:08.000Z","msg":"推到佢落地獄"},{"pid":"ecd099b9424c3ae9ce3a446b98436f053c498f2a","tid":1278300,"uid":152432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:02:38.000Z","msg":"推到佢比狗雞姦"},{"pid":"b68d2aa44861a29df3a4e0328f68584aa8d453e3","tid":1278300